x=U\Sigma V^T
\|x\|_*=tr(\sqrt{x^Tx})=tr(\sqrt{(U\Sigma V^T)^T(U\Sigma V^T)})
\Rightarrow \|x\|_*=tr(\sqrt{V\Sigma U^T U\Sigma V^T})=tr(\sqrt{V\Sigma^2V^T})
\Rightarrow \|x\|_*=tr(\sqrt{V^TV\Sigma^2})=tr(\sqrt{V^TV\Sigma^2})=tr(\sqrt{\Sigma^2})=tr(|\Sigma|)
